snippet.title: Facewound (Windows game 2006)
snippet.description:
Facewound is a very exciting zombie action game.
The aim of the game is that the main character get rid of zombies and find a sky-blue flame to the next level.

In the game, you can use a slow motion function.
but if you lack your energy, you can't utilize it.
On top of that, if you do away with a zombie, you can get plutonium bars.
If the plutonium progress bar filled up, you can get a credit.
Using your own credits, you can buy items.
